comments: Covington (POR) slightly extends his arms toward Caruso's (LAL) front as he sets the pick and marginal contact occurs as he releases to roll.
Lillard (POR) brings his off-arm toward Caruso's (LAL) front and marginal contact occurs as Lillard naturally releases away.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) extends his hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Nurkic's (POR) right arm after he releases the pass.
Davis (LAL) cleanly blocks Covington's (POR) dunk attempt.
McLemore (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball before incidental contact occurs with Covington's (POR) left arm during rebounding.
Davis (LAL) re-establishes in bounds before gaining control of the rebound.
Covington (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Davis (LAL) in transition.
Covington (POR) moves slightly forward toward Davis (LAL) and marginal contact occurs with Davis' backside during rebounding.
Nurkic (POR) legally contests Davis' (LAL) put-back attempt and avoids making contact with Davis.
Nurkic (POR) firms up in his screening position in Caruso's (LAL) path and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) moves alongside McCollum's (POR) path with his arm collapsed to his front and marginal contact occurs with McCollum's side/arm at the end of the drive.
Kuzma (LAL) avoids making contact with the ball as he brings his hand into the netting and does not cause the ball to take an unnatural bounce.
Davis (LAL) brushes Covington's (POR) left arm and marginal contact occurs during the follow-through of Covington's put-back attempt.
Covington (POR) initiates contact with Davis' (LAL) lower half and front, dislodging Davis from his position before making any contact with the ball.
Davis (LAL) moves alongside Nurkic's (POR) path to the basket and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Lillard (POR) and Kuzma (LAL) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each attempt to gain control of the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) moves laterally and delivers body contact to Lillard (POR) that affects his SQBR.
Kuzma (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Powell's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Powell's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
McCollum (POR) and McLemore (LAL) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another near the perimeter.
McLemore (LAL) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Lillard's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Lillard (POR) and Kuzma (LAL) engage and disengage with one another as Kuzma moves over the screen.
Powell (POR) moves somewhat forward toward Caruso (LAL) and marginal body contact occurs as Caruso is gathering the ball, which Powell absorbs.
Davis (LAL) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Caruso (LAL) veers slightly toward Hollis-Jefferson (POR) following the hand-off and absorbs the body contact that occurs.
Covington (POR) legally contests Kuzma's (LAL) layup attempt and incidental "high-five" contact occurs with Kuzma after the release.
